{
  "title": "Xtra Dense Australian Chicken Skewers",
  "description": "A citrusy and dense Australian dish featuring anchovy fillet, tandoor, and ayurvedic-rajasic-friendly ingredients, perfect for a weeknight dinner",
  "cuisine": "Australian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
